        "share_text": "Where are our kegs?? Get yourself to the pub on Saturday for our Gym Stuff For Non-Gym Folks with our pals @valkyrienewcastle !!\n\nYou get beer on arrival @younghenrys , expert gym stuff @omgitscoachhugo, sweet chunes @just.bonnie.anne, and post workout brunch @theoak.tigheshill.\n\n$30 tickets \u00e2\u0080\u0094 all proceeds to our friends @aconhunter.\n\nLink in bio, pals \u00f0\u009f\u0091\u00af\u00e2\u0080\u008d\u00e2\u0099\u0080\u00ef\u00b8\u008f\n\n#strengthisforeveryone",
        "original_content_owner": "theoak.tigheshill"
      },
