    {
      "sender_name": "The Oak Tighes Hill",
      "timestamp_ms": 1770164501075,
      "content": "You sent an attachment.",
      "share": {
        "link": "https://www.instagram.com/reel/DUUMENKk8wh/?id=3824735049116535841_29666268335",
        "share_text": "HOW DO WE RATE JOSH\u00e2\u0080\u0099S FORM?? \n\nAre you gym-curious? Wanting to start a bit of a health kick in a comfortable space, while also incorporating beer? Gym Stuff for Non-Gym People might be the event you\u00e2\u0080\u0099ve been looking for\u00e2\u0080\u00a6\n\nOn Saturday, Feb 28th from 11am - 1pm, the team from Valkyrie Gym will turn the Oak into a place of exercise, teaching basic and practical gym techniques to the soundtrack of music by DJ Bonnie Ann.\n\nYou\u00e2\u0080\u0099ll get a free Young Henrys or Heaps Normal on arrival, and you\u00e2\u0080\u0099ll leave with a four-week exercise plan.\n\nPerfect excuse to skip work for the day!\n\nTickets are $30 (or a small donation) with proceeds going to ACON Hunter. Hit the link in bio to grab a ticket!",
        "original_content_owner": "theoak.tigheshill"
      },
